snippet.textDisplay: While I do love this song and the whole cultural aspect of it... Our culture is very important but holding on to it so tightly will only lose its value. Traditions and values that changed with the world are the ones that are still existing. I am glad to belong to the land which integrated and accepted all kinds of trends, cultures, backgrounds even if it was very different from our old traditionals. The only way ahead is moving on from the past and educating each other about our desi history and cultures and finding new ways how we can still push them down to our future generations without keeping them stagnant in our society as older people have. because honestly thats not very possible.
